Might as well just disable any summoners that aren't exaust/ignite/flash for the support then, and limit them to a community endorsed champion pool. Less the class that has been MUST INCLUDE in every season of this game, the ranged ADC feel offended that they must alter their play. After all, the bot lane is all about them. We can't have them feeling slighted by the fucking peasants in the support slot.

{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}} 


This ban will do nothing to get more people playing support. Its just going make willing players even more rare.
